#### What is the expected behavior?

Proper `<mat-select>` position.

#### What is the current behavior?

Position of `<mat-select>` is wrong because the overlay `min-width` calculation is wrong. If I understand correctly
```
min-width = this.trigger.nativeElement.getBoundingClientRect().width;
overlay width = min-width + 2 * padding
```

and the result looks like:

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1329824/57008453-5fd3e480-6c01-11e9-9e60-e306c686b9f2.png)

Probably the `min-width` should be `this.trigger.nativeElement.getBoundingClientRect().width - 2*padding`

